+/************************************************************************/
+/*                                                                      */
+/*  PROJECT : exFAT & FAT12/16/32 File System                           */
+/*  FILE    : exfat_blkdev.c                                            */
+/*  PURPOSE : exFAT Block Device Driver Glue Layer                      */
+/*                                                                      */
